ygData.messageBody:
welcome!

well i can never remember which ser4vers are wich, but i do know that there is the Ordo Ursi Prismatus on the Lanys t'vyl server (spelling??) we were basicly an all bears guild, but now we have evolved into a GBLT and friends guild, give us a cheack out :) the address to our website is

http://www.eqordo.com/ that is to our main page, it is new, our old page lost its provider or something similar

http://pub37.ezboard.com/bordo that is to our message board, drop a line to us there and you will be able to find out the exact process of joining :)

happy hunting :)

----- Original Message -----
From: flmage@...
Sent: Sunday, July 08, 2001 1:30 PM
To: EQ_rainbow@yahoogroups.com
Subject: [EQ_rainbow] Hail All

Should have done this sooner ... been playing EQ since Christmas on
Torv and though I have to say I have fun ... sometimes it can be
irriating with some of the people ... I see that there are some guild
on the other servers that have been built and was just wondering if
anyone could tell me if they were still in place ... Have a real hard
time giving up a 47 wiz but I think it would be nice to play with
family and would like to try ... If u could please let me know what
guilds are on what servers and see if I can't hook up with some of u
in game ... til then ... Be safe and good killing always
